{"title":"金花飞溅","authors":["王术"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":1,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金花飞溅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王术"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一幅大红捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万点钢花镶边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写上钢铁工人的喜悦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向亲爱的毛主席问安！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四年的朝阳啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请照进我们不夜的车间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜班工人在举行喜宴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎一个新世界的春天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转炉里倾出琼浆玉液，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天车执壶殷勤敬献，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每向钢模斟一杯红酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筵前满是金花飞溅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓风机吹起悦耳的长号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉膛内响着密集的鼓点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残渣在烈火中消失，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵观钢水风云变幻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转炉像高燃的明烛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金辉飞出石景山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机床、钢轨、拖拉机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着亮光热情呼唤。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}